{"tid":705383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【回顧中共柒事】20/5 劉鶴︰不打貿易戰　停止互相加徵關稅","createTime":"2018-06-17T06:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T07:28:29.000Z","uid":173631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b51d53192d988292ff1f1429eaff186893110796","tid":705383,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T06:07:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180520/bknint-20180520030155196-0520_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180520%2Fbknint-20180520030155196-0520_17011_001.html&d=Ojbc0A%2FW3oBEYucFl%2BAUDJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=98c48d2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180520/bknint-20180520030155196-0520_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國國務院副總理劉鶴率領的中方代表團，連日來與美國代表團磋商後，當地時間上周六（19日）終發表聯合聲明。中國官媒報道，劉鶴當天上午接受媒體採訪時表示，此次中美經貿磋商的最大成果，是雙方達成共識，不打貿易戰，並停止互相加徵關稅，又形容是中美「雙贏」的結果。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n劉鶴指出，此次是「積極、務實、富有建設性和成果」的訪問，雙方就發展積極健康的經貿關係達成許多共識；中美雙方將在能源、農產品、醫療、高科技產品、金融等領域加強合作，不但可推動中國經濟轉向高質量發展，亦有利於美方削減貿易赤字，「是雙贏的選擇」。另中美雙方亦會加強相互投資，同時深化知識產權保護領域的合作，有利於全球經濟貿易的穩定繁榮。<br />\n<br />\n劉鶴強調，中國有龐大的中等收入群體，將成為世界最大的市場，而這個市場具高度競爭性，出口國必須要提高自己產品和服務的競爭力，才能在中國市場獲得份額；他補充，中國不僅願意從美國進口，亦將從全世界進口。<br />\n<br />\n劉鶴提到，此次雙方取得共識是有其「必然性」，但必須認識到「冰凍三尺非一日之寒」，解決兩國經貿關係多年來的結構性問題需要時間；但他認為，中美經貿關係健康發展，是符合歷史潮流，「無人能擋」，面對未來兩國關係發展中可能遇到的新曲折新矛盾，必須「冷靜看待，堅持對話，妥善處理」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">笑撚死</span></span>"},{"pid":"7a4432f8cb1961d146f091ca3703ab0925ce6de6","tid":705383,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T06:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e7fd810d3060f823ceeca083a9d9d3991e9372","tid":705383,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T07:24:40.000Z","msg":"不要打啦！會死的了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa471225383cee90a84b9141611c831be23a93e","tid":705383,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T07:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mf599y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMf599y.gif&h=c3f1a031&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6dfbe836d46b166c0888be3dab52adc192e7f3c","tid":705383,"uid":68285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 劉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n佢去美帝傾係為自己升官發財鋪路咋<br />\n你估真係為贏國人民<br />\n最大贏家就係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}